      "content": "is it just me or does the power grid hum sound... different lately?? like its not just a constant buzz anymore. its got this weird rhythmic pulse to it. almost like it's modulated. i feel it in my chest more than i hear it with my ears whenever it hits that specific frequency. u think thats normal for electrical transformers??",
